<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <style>
      body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-family:
      'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; } .container { max-width:
      620px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #dddddd; } h2 { color: #2c3e50;
      font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; } p { line-height: 1.6; color:
      #4a4a4a; } .details { margin-top: 20px; } .details li { list-style: none;
      padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee; } .details span {
      font-weight: 600; } .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.9em; color:
      #888888; text-align: center; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Meeting Confirmation</h2>
      <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
      <p>Thank you for scheduling a meeting with us. Below are the details of
        your appointment:</p>

      <ul class="details">
        <li><span>Name:</span> {{name}}</li>
        <li><span>Email:</span> {{email}}</li>
        <li><span>Phone:</span> {{phone}}</li>
        <li><span>Meeting Type:</span> {{meetingType}}</li>
        <li><span>Date:</span> {{date}}</li>
        <li><span>Time:</span> {{time}}</li>
        <li><span>Additional Info:</span> {{information}}</li>
      </ul>

      <p>We look forward to connecting with you soon.</p>

      <div class="footer">
        You received this email because you scheduled a meeting via our website.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>